      "n": 21,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tai Deena turrehs\njebkursch kahdu Gohtinu / un\nkahdus diwi fihkus Lohpus.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 22,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tatschutee tik dauds Pee-\nna dohs / ka tas Sweestu eh-\ndihs/ jo ikkatrs/ kas pahri valiks\ntai Semmê/ tas ehdihg Swee-\nstu un Meddu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 23,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ir tai Deena notiks / ka\nikkatrâ Weetâ/ kur tuhktoschi\nWihna Rohkt bijuschi/ kas tuhk-\nstoschus Sudraba Gabbalus\nmakfaja/ turpatt buhs Ehrfschki\nun Dadschi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 24,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ka ar Bultahm un Stoh-\npeim tur buhs ja-eet / jo wiffâ\njahs pahr Rezinu un Remaliju\ntai Semmê buhs Ehrfschki un\nDadschi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 25,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ir us wiffeem teem Kal-\nneem/ kas zittkahrt ar Kapleem\ntappe kappati/ ne weens warrehs\nnahkt no Bihjaschanas preeksch\nEhrfschkeem un Dadscheem/ bet\ntur taps leeli Lohpt ganniti/ un\nfihki Lohpi to famihdihs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tas KUNGS fazzija\nus man: Jemmees weenu leelu\nfatihnu Grahnatu/ un raksti us\nto ar Zilweka Rakstamo/ steidsee\nus Laupijumu tu tschaklis Lau-\npitajs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 2,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad nehmu es jewim us-\ntizzamus Leezinekus/ Uriju te\nPreesteri/ un Sakariju Jeberc-\nrijus Dehlu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un es gahju pee tahs *Pra*\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "weetenes/ un ta tappe gruhta/\nun djeindeja weenu Dehlu. Ui\ntas KUNGS fazzija us man:\nNofanz wianna Wahrdiu / Stei-\ndsees us Laupijumu tu tschaklis\nLaupitajs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Jo pirinis tas Puutens-\nwarr faukt / mans Tehws jel-\nmanna Mahte / tad taps ta-\nSpehks no Damascus / un tas\nLaupijums no Samarijas no-\nnests preeksch to Kehniku no Af-\ntirijas.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tas KUNGS runnaj-\nwehl us man/ un fazzija:\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tapehz ka schre Paudi-\nnizzina to Uhdent no Siloas-\nkas weeglinam tekk / un preeza-\njahs pahr Rezinu un Remaliju\nDehlu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Redsi/ tad liks tas KUNG-\npahr teem uskahpt to sitpru u-\nwarrenu Uppes Uhdent/ to Ket-\nnizu no Afirijas/ un wiffu wi-\nna Gohdibu/ un wisch zeltee-\npahr wiffahm winnu Upvehm-\nun ees pahr wiffahm winn-\nMallahm.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un wisch zaurt ees u-\nJuha/ un pahrpluhdihs to/ u-\nees zauri/ un fneegfees lthydspa-\n* Kaflam/ un wisch issteeps-\nwus † Spahrnus/ un peepildi-\ntawu plattu Semmi/ ak Im-\nmanuel!\n"
    }
  ],
